Title: Frontolimbic atrophy is associated with agitation and aggression in mild cognitive impairment and Alzheimer's disease
Journal: Alzheimer's and Dementia
Volume: 9
Issue: 5 SUPPL.
Pages: S95-S104
Short Title: Frontolimbic atrophy is associated with agitation and aggression in mild cognitive impairment and Alzheimer's disease
ISSN: 15525260 (ISSN)
DOI: 10.1016/j.jalz.2012.10.005
